data.name: lblInstructions.Text
data.value: Input your desired username and password in to the following fields Usernames must be between 3 and 16 character long Passwords much contain at least 1 number, 1 lowercase and 1 uppercase letter. Insert your First and last names in to the textboxes provided. Choose an avatar from the drop down list When your ready click on "Submit Details" No fields can be left blank If your registration was sucessfull you will recieve a message to confirm this. You are now able to log on from the main start screen using the details entered
